New features
#12000
: Support safe or unsafe autocorrect config for LSP. (
@koic
)
Bug fixes
#12005
: Fix a false negative for
Lint/Debugger
when using debugger method inside lambda. (
@koic
)
#11986
: Fix a false positive for
Lint/MixedCaseRange
when the number of characters at the start or end of range is other than 1. (
@koic
)
#11992
